{
/* Data Lookup Key - Specifies how to replace text found inside curly braces

  {{Variable}} Generate new Ids using a DisplayName from the variable's matching .txt file in substitutions/
	$ - DisplayName of a Lua variable with VariableAutoFormat formatting (minus exceptions from NeverFormat table)
	@ - DisplayName of a Lua variable with ItemName formatting
	* - DisplayName of a Lua variable with automatic red/green coloring for modified stat values
  % - Full Description of a Lua variable
  ^ - Description only of a Lua variable
  + - Description only of a Lua variable
	! - Texture of the path stored in a Lua variable
	JU - Texture of button mapped to the Jump Control for the current platform and input type
	... (Other Control symbols defined in Controls.cs) */

